---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About DevSuite — Free Developer Utility Hub"
  description="Learn about DevSuite, a free all-in-one developer and creator utility platform built for speed and simplicity."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About DevSuite</h1>

    <h2>What is DevSuite?</h2>
    <p>DevSuite is a free, open collection of essential developer and creator utilities built for speed, simplicity, and privacy. Every tool runs entirely in your browser — we never transmit, store, or process your data on any server.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe developer tools should be instantly accessible, blazing fast, and free of unnecessary friction. No accounts. No downloads. No data collection. Just open a tab and get to work.</p>

    <h2>The Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/case-converter"><strong>Text Case Converter</strong></a>: Transform text between UPPERCASE, lowercase, Title Case, and Sentence case with a single click.</li>
      <li><a href="/lorem-ipsum"><strong>Lorem Ipsum Generator</strong></a>: Generate placeholder text by paragraphs, sentences, or words for your designs and mockups.</li>
      <li><a href="/word-counter"><strong>Word Counter</strong></a>: Count words, characters, sentences, paragraphs, and analyze text.</li>
      <li><a href="/markdown-preview"><strong>Markdown Previewer</strong></a>: Write Markdown and see a live HTML preview instantly.</li>
      <li><a href="/json-formatter"><strong>JSON Formatter</strong></a>: Format, validate, beautify, and minify JSON data instantly.</li>
      <li><a href="/base64"><strong>Base64 Encoder / Decoder</strong></a>: Encode text to Base64 or decode Base64 to plain text with full Unicode support.</li>
      <li><a href="/uuid-generator"><strong>UUID Generator</strong></a>: Generate single or bulk random UUID v4 identifiers instantly.</li>
      <li><a href="/regex-tester"><strong>Regex Tester</strong></a>: Test and debug regular expressions with real-time match highlighting.</li>
      <li><a href="/px-to-rem"><strong>PX ↔ REM Converter</strong></a>: A bidirectional pixel-to-REM calculator with configurable base font size.</li>
      <li><a href="/color-converter"><strong>Color Converter</strong></a>: Convert between HEX, RGB, HSL, and HSB color formats with a visual color picker.</li>
      <li><a href="/css-gradient"><strong>CSS Gradient Generator</strong></a>: Create beautiful linear and radial CSS gradients with a visual editor.</li>
      <li><a href="/box-shadow"><strong>Box Shadow Generator</strong></a>: Create perfect CSS drop shadows with multiple layer support.</li>
      <li><a href="/jwt-decoder"><strong>JWT Decoder</strong></a>: Decode and inspect JSON Web Tokens to view header, payload, and verify expiration.</li>
      <li><a href="/hash-generator"><strong>Hash Generator</strong></a>: Generate MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, and SHA-512 hashes from text using the Web Crypto API.</li>
      <li><a href="/password-generator"><strong>Password Generator</strong></a>: Generate cryptographically strong, random passwords with a built-in strength meter.</li>
      <li><a href="/text-encrypt"><strong>Text Encryptor</strong></a>: Encrypt and decrypt messages using AES-256-GCM.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Built With</h2>
    <p>DevSuite is built with modern web technologies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Astro</strong> — Static site generator for maximum performance</li>
      <li><strong>CSS</strong> — Custom vanilla CSS with zero framework overhead</li>
      <li><strong>Vanilla JavaScript</strong> — Fast, native logic for all tools</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Every page is statically generated at build time, resulting in sub-second load times and a perfect Lighthouse score.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Have feedback, suggestions, or want to report a bug? Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
